## DIZAYN QOIDALARI
- Faqat Dark theme — Light mode yo'q
- Font: Onest — boshqa font HECH QACHON
- Gradient: har doim `from-accent to-accent-2`
- Active state: `active:scale-[0.97]` yoki `active:scale-[0.98]`
- Transition: `transition-all duration-150` — tez bo'lishi kerak
- Glassmorphism: `bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-md`
- Shimmer: `animate-shimmer` Skeleton uchun
